WEBVTT

00:10:59.630 --> 00:11:01.982
a noose around his neck

00:11:02.006 --> 00:11:04.243
and a blindfold over his eyes.

00:11:05.736 --> 00:11:07.207
Samereh Alinejad

00:11:07.231 --> 00:11:11.244
had been given the sole right
under the laws of her country

00:11:11.268 --> 00:11:14.133
to either pardon this man

00:11:14.157 --> 00:11:16.323
or initiate his execution.

00:11:17.188 --> 00:11:19.648
Put another way, she could pardon him

00:11:19.672 --> 00:11:23.216
or literally push that chair
out from underneath his feet.

00:11:25.521 --> 00:11:26.671
(Exhales)

00:11:27.926 --> 00:11:29.076
I just ...

00:11:29.633 --> 00:11:33.562
I can't picture the agony
going through both Samereh and this man